reviewText: I'm an elementary school teacher and I love this video series for my students. Beautiful videos that help with students who may have creative blocks or apprehension with art education. This series of short videos approximately 5 minutes each it Is also a great way to fill-in those last-minute time gaps. These are high-quality videos that I would recommend them to my peers.
This is a great video!  I bought another one for the art teacher.  It has The Dot, Ish, Art (a great story) and two others.  The students love it.
